name: Roshambo
description: Roshambo - The Next Generation AI Based Social Platform The goal is to bring people closer to each other in a more fun and engaging way. So we decided to Gamify the social space. Roshambo will be the place where people can be themselves. Find and connect with people who interests you and share the same interests as yours. We want to open up dating, professional, community space outside of just plain texting and make it more real by bringing Roshambo world in Metaverse where they can do all the things they would do in real world. Like grab a beer at a bar, going to a games event, or sitting in a lounge, make friends or party in a disco club...endless possibilities of what you can do with people you meet in Roshambo.
